62
00:04:55,734 --> 00:04:58,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No cars ahead! Drift through it!</b></font>

63
00:05:10,654 --> 00:05:12,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I couldn't be my usual self</i></b></font>

64
00:05:12,824 --> 00:05:16,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>because I was too conscious of him.</i></b></font>

65
00:05:16,024 --> 00:05:18,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Deep down, I believed that no racer</i></b></font>

66
