81
00:06:24,264 --> 00:06:27,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow, it started!</b></font>

82
00:06:29,394 --> 00:06:32,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My name is Mako Sato.</b></font>

83
