<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Good job, Mako. You're right on.</i></b></font>

117
00:09:55,434 --> 00:09:57,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Drift right through here!</b></font>

118
00:10:23,664 --> 00:10:26,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No cars ahead! Drift again!</b></font>

119
00:10:34,714 --> 00:10:38,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Amazing. Maybe too amazing...</i></b></font>

120
00:10:38,884 --> 00:10:44,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Good racers always leave room for error.</i></b></font>

121
00:10:44,684 --> 00:10:47,924
