146
00:14:42,994 --> 00:14:44,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Why not?</i></b></font>

147
00:14:46,994 --> 00:14:49,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako, you're going in too sharp!</b></font>

148
00:15:05,414 --> 00:15:08,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can't recover! Spin away from him!</b></font>

149
00:15:11,284 --> 00:15:13,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Oh, man!</i></b></font>

150
00:15:13,084 --> 00:15:15,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Please don't hit us!</i></b></font>

151
00:16:01,134 --> 00:16:04,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--We're saved.
--Brilliant.</b></font>

