<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's so skilled...</b></font>

154
00:16:09,714 --> 00:16:12,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...that I almost hate him.</b></font>

155
00:16:15,154 --> 00:16:16,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How do you feel?</b></font>

156
00:16:19,924 --> 00:16:22,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We lost...</b></font>

157
00:16:22,254 --> 00:16:24,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but I feel very satisfied.</b></font>

158
00:16:26,164 --> 00:16:32,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It reminded me of the excitement
I felt when I first started racing.</b></font>

159
00:16:42,014 --> 00:16:46,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We would practice until sunrise.</b></font>

160
00:16:46,514 --> 00:16:50,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That same pure sensation...</b></font>

161
00:16:53,024 --> 00:16:55,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You went too far at the end,</b></font>

162
00:16:55,924 --> 00:16:58,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but you were great until then.</b></font>

163
00:16:58,594 --> 00:17:02,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The best race ever.</b></font>

164
00:17:02,294 --> 00:17:04,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sayuki...</b></font>

165
00:17:04,134 --> 00:17:08,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whatever you decide to do from now on,</b></font>

166
00:17:08,274 --> 00:17:10,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>just know that you have my blessing.</b></font>

167
00:17:12,604 --> 00:17:14,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks, Sayuki.</b></font>

168
00:17:14,944 --> 00:17:17,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No need for tears, Mako.</b></font>

169
00:17:17,614 --> 00:17:20,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's just enjoy this glorious moment.</b></font>

170
00:17:33,624 --> 00:17:35,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're back!</b></font>

171
00:17:43,134 --> 00:17:45,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder how the race went?</b></font>

172
00:17:45,504 --> 00:17:49,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You think they're going again?</b></font>

173
00:17:49,514 --> 00:17:51,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Probably...</b></font>

174
00:17:56,414 --> 00:17:58,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

175
00:18:07,424 --> 00:18:08,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi...</b></font>

176
00:18:08,764 --> 00:18:10,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I find it hard to believe, but...</b></font>

177
00:18:10,964 --> 00:18:14,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess we won't need the second race, huh?</b></font>

178
00:18:16,204 --> 00:18:19,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No second race. It's all over.</b></font>

179
00:18:21,144 --> 00:18:22,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I knew it.</b></font>

180
00:18:22,444 --> 00:18:24,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even for Takumi...</b></font>

181
00:18:24,684 --> 00:18:32,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No... I didn't want to see him lose like this.</b></font>

182
00:18:35,124 --> 00:18:37,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We lost.</b></font>

183
00:18:37,824 --> 00:18:39,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come again?</b></font>

184
00:18:39,994 --> 00:18:42,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What did you just say?</b></font>

185
00:18:42,234 --> 00:18:45,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I said we lost.</b></font>

186
00:18:45,304 --> 00:18:47,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't make me repeat it.</b></font>

187
00:18:47,334 --> 00:18:49,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's the winner.</b></font>

188
00:18:49,304 --> 00:18:51,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

189
00:18:55,144 --> 00:19:02,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yay!
--Wow!</b></font>

190
00:19:09,424 --> 00:19:13,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I never imagined we could
lose on our own turf.</b></font>

191
00:19:13,864 --> 00:19:18,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All I did was follow you,
and I barely did that,</b></font>

192
00:19:18,904 --> 00:19:22,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I don't think I really won the race.</b></font>

193
00:19:22,404 --> 00:19:24,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't be so modest.</b></font>

194
00:19:24,774 --> 00:19:29,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With your skills, you have
the right to rub it in.</b></font>

195
00:19:30,614 --> 00:19:31,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...</b></font>

196
00:19:31,944 --> 00:19:34,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've put in hours of practice here,</b></font>

197
00:19:34,684 --> 00:19:37,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so we were very confident.</b></font>

198
00:19:37,384 --> 00:19:40,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You chose to chase us,</b></font>

199
00:19:40,424 --> 00:19:43,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and we couldn't shake you off.</b></font>

200
00:19:43,024 --> 00:19:45,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We accept our defeat, right, Mako?</b></font>

201
00:19:45,424 --> 00:19:47,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

202
00:19:47,964 --> 00:19:49,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mako...</i></b></font>

203
00:19:53,134 --> 00:19:55,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was by far the best race ever.</b></font>

204
00:19:55,974 --> 00:19:57,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks.</b></font>

205
00:20:09,984 --> 00:20:12,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're blushing big time.</b></font>

206
00:20:15,124 --> 00:20:16,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a mystery.</b></font>

207
00:20:16,994 --> 00:20:20,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your racing ability is extraordinary,</b></font>

208
00:20:20,564 --> 00:20:22,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but otherwise you barely seem ordinary.</b></font>

209
00:20:22,934 --> 00:20:25,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is how he usually is.</b></font>

210
00:20:25,134 --> 00:20:26,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When he's not racing,</b></font>

211
00:20:26,934 --> 00:20:30,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we can't tell if he's awake or asleep.</b></font>

212
00:20:30,504 --> 00:20:32,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, thanks a lot.</b></font>

213
00:20:32,674 --> 00:20:34,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki's right, though.</b></font>

214
00:20:34,474 --> 00:20:39,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyhow, I'm amazed how
young and good you really are.</b></font>

215
00:20:44,854 --> 00:20:47,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You should give it another try.</i></b></font>

216
00:20:47,024 --> 00:20:50,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You'd be a fool to let her go so easily.</i></b></font>

217
00:20:53,324 --> 00:20:55,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani.</b></font>

218
00:20:58,604 --> 00:21:03,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you for tonight...</b></font>

219
00:21:03,674 --> 00:21:08,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako, I...</b></font>

220
00:21:08,114 --> 00:21:10,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't be depressed, Iketani!</b></font>

221
00:21:10,474 --> 00:21:13,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Racers don't need girls, right?</b></font>

222
00:21:21,824 --> 00:21:23,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right...</b></font>

223
00:21:27,194 --> 00:21:32,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Actually, he has a really adorable face.</i></b></font>

224
00:21:32,704 --> 00:21:36,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, what's your name, anyway?</b></font>

225
00:21:36,504 --> 00:21:41,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Takumi Fujiwara...
--Itsuki Takeuchi, 18!</b></font>

226
00:21:41,514 --> 00:21:44,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm an Aries and type O,
and my favorite car is...</b></font>

227
00:21:44,644 --> 00:21:48,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think I asked you...</b></font>

228
00:21:51,524 --> 00:21:54,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, since we're friends now,</b></font>

229
00:21:54,524 --> 00:21:57,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>how about going swimming
together sometime?</b></font>

230
00:21:57,394 --> 00:21:59,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That sounds great!</b></font>

231
00:21:59,594 --> 00:22:01,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kenji?</b></font>

232
00:22:01,594 --> 00:22:05,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Sure.
--How about you, Takumi?</b></font>

233
00:22:05,504 --> 00:22:09,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah...
--You, too, Iketani?</b></font>

234
00:22:09,674 --> 00:22:15,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yay! Thank you, Sayuki!</b></font>

235
00:22:16,274 --> 00:22:22,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go wild and crazy with my Eight-Five!</b></font>

236
00:22:34,524 --> 00:22:40,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There was a time when I</i>
<i>wandered aimlessly, tired of love</i></b></font>

237
00:22:40,364 --> 00:22:48,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I lost sight of myself and gave in to desire</i></b></font>

238
00:22:48,214 --> 00:22:54,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But destiny is ever-changing</i></b></font>

239
00:22:54,614 --> 00:23:02,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And charmed by innocent eyes</i></b></font>

240
00:23:03,624 --> 00:23:10,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bloom like a red rose,</i>
<i>I hold you ever so tightly</i></b></font>

241
00:23:10,164 --> 00:23:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All I can say is that I believe</i>
<i>my feelings are true</i></b></font>

242
00:23:16,974 --> 00:23:22,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's enjoy our happiness...</i></b></font>

243
00:23:22,144 --> 00:23:29,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Into our shining future</i></b></font>

244
00:23:41,194 --> 00:23:48,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We'll prove countless times...</i></b></font>

245
00:23:48,874 --> 00:23:54,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Our passion will last for eternity!</i></b></font>

246
00:23:54,944 --> 00:24:01,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bloom like a red rose,</i>
<i>I embrace you ever so tightly</i></b></font>

247
00:24:01,614 --> 00:24:08,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if I lose everything that I have,</i>
<i>I will never let you go</i></b></font>

248
00:24:08,454 --> 00:24:13,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bloom, my beautiful...</i></b></font>

249
00:24:13,694 --> 00:24:20,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...and miraculous flower</i></b></font>

250
00:24:26,644 --> 00:24:30,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If men weren't honest with themselves,</i></b></font>

251
00:24:30,044 --> 00:24:32,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>mankind would've been extinct long ago.</i></b></font>

252
00:24:32,884 --> 00:24:34,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You're right, boss!</i></b></font>

253
00:24:34,714 --> 00:24:37,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The beginning of a relationship is important.</i></b></font>

254
00:24:37,154 --> 00:24:39,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Make sure that you don't...</i></b></font>

255
00:24:41,254 --> 00:24:45,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hi, Honey. I'm on my way...</i></b></font>

256
00:24:45,264 --> 00:24:48,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Leaving, boss? Make sure you don't what?</i></b></font>

257
00:24:48,264 --> 00:24:52,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next on Initial D: "The End of Summer."</i></b></font>

258
00:24:52,004 --> 00:24:55,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Make sure you don't miss it!</i></b></font>

